---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How this site handles analytics, cookies, and comments."
  eyebrow="Legal"
  crumbs={[{ label: 'Privacy' }]}
>
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <p>This site is a static personal website. It does not collect personal data beyond what is described below.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      This site may use Google Analytics 4 to understand aggregate traffic patterns (pages viewed, referrers,
      approximate location). No personally identifiable information is collected or sold.
    </p>
    <h2>Comments</h2>
    <p>
      Blog comments are powered by <a href="https://giscus.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Giscus</a>, which
      stores comments as GitHub Discussions in the site's repository. Giscus requires you to sign in with a
      GitHub account to comment; GitHub's own privacy policy applies to that interaction.
    </p>
    <h2>Third-party embeds</h2>
    <p>
      This site displays live repository, language, and category data fetched client-side from the public
      GitHub API. No data is sent to GitHub beyond a standard read-only API request.
    </p>
    <p>
      The "Book on Topmate" / "Get in touch!" buttons link out to
      <a href="https://topmate.io/sarveshtalele" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Topmate</a>, a third-party
      scheduling service. Topmate's own privacy policy applies once you follow that link.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to talelesarvesh@gmail.com.</p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
